      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:4:72:7",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/71/5394",
      "text": [
        ":\nقُلْتُ لِأَبِي اَلْحَسَنِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ اَلْمَرْأَةُ تَخَافُ اَلْحَبَلَ فَتَشْرَبُ اَلدَّوَاءَ فَتُلْقِي مَا فِي بَطْنِهَا فَقَالَ \"لاَ\"\nفَقُلْتُ إِنَّمَا هُوَ نُطْفَةٌ قَالَ \"إِنَّ أَوَّلَ مَا يُخْلَقُ نُطْفَةٌ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5394 - Al-Husayn ibn Said narrated from Ibn Abi Umayr from Muhammad ibn Abi Hamzah and Husayn Al-Rawwasi from Ishaq ibn Ammar, who said:\nI asked Abu Al-Hasan (as) about a woman who fears pregnancy and drinks medicine to cause a miscarriage.\nImam (as) replied: \"No.\"\nI said: \"It is only a drop of fluid (nutfah).\"\nImam (as) said: \"Indeed, the first stage of creation is a drop of fluid (nutfah).\""
        ]
      }
    },
